OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry but cloudy to start.
OL,6,FRain will soon push north through the
OL,7,Fmorning. Staying cloudy with outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain and strong southeast winds
OL,9,Fthroughout the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying mostly cloudy with
OL,12,Fshowery outbreaks of rain through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight. Some drier,
OL,14,Fclearer spells developing for a time
OL,15,Ffor Orkney overnight. Strong southeast
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FCloudy to start for
OL,19,FShetland. Otherwise bright spells and
OL,20,Fscattered showers, these heavy and
OL,21,Fperhaps thundery at times. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
