OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,6,Fstart Friday with rain pushing east
OL,7,Flater. Bright spells and showers on
OL,8,FSaturday. Mostly dry, bright Sunday,
OL,9,Fchance of the odd shower.
